General.Name: Airtime Partecipazioni SpA
General.Description: Mexedia Società Per Azioni S.B. provides wholesale telecommunications and business services. The company was formerly known as Airtime Partecipazioni S.p.A. and changed its name to Mexedia Società Per Azioni S.B. in May 2022. Mexedia Società Per Azioni S.B. was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Rome, Italy.
General.Address: Via Di Affogalasino 105, Rome, RM, Italy, 00148
